Canon Pixma TS9120

Enter Printer Model


How to do canon ts9120 wireless setup

When we talk about Canon TS9120 we are talking about a printer that is compatible with Bluetooth, WIFI, and plugged internet connection. So without further adieu, let’s get to know how wireless connection can be set up for canon TS910

Canon ts9120 Setup

Two key components are ij.start.canon ts9120. Link your home network first to the printer. Then, download and set up drivers to command the printer on your computer.

Set up the Wireless Link

  • Attach the printer to and trigger the power supply. The power lamp is illuminated, you must check. If the printer is wiping, print head orientation, etc., wait if this is done.
  • On the left-hand side of the display screen, you can see a menu tab. The house icon is marked.
  • This Menu tab must be pressed. If an error screen is given, press OK and press again the button Menu.
  • In the left corner of the bottom of the screen, there will be a Wireless Connection tab. To open the wireless screen, press it.
  • From the different options available, click on the LAN Settings tab.
  • On the next page, click the Wireless LAN tab.
  • Opt for the Wireless LAN Configuration on the next computer.
  • In the Wireless LAN setup, pick Simple Wireless Link.
  • Fast Wireless Communication is possible for Canon Pixma TS9120 Printer. It will take some time and it may momentarily become difficult to connect to the Internet.
  • Settings on a device or smartphone can be confirmed on the next screen. To validate this, you have to tap “Yes.”
  • The setup will take a few minutes now. If your printer is finalized, the next screen will be shown telling you to continue on your computer, your smartphone, and the ij.start.canon ts9120. Back to the computer of the program.

Set up the wired link

  • Attach the printer to and trigger the power supply. The power lamp is illuminated, you must check. Wait if the printer does some cleaning operation, print head orientation, etc. Wait.
  • To configure the printer, you would need an Ethernet cable. It is not normally part of the Canon Printer kit. Therefore, you have to get it in advance.
  • On the left-hand side at the back of your printer, you have to find the Ethernet port. Drop port lock. Port cap removed.
  • The Printer and Network Interface should be connected to i.e. Ethernet cable firewall. router. It is important to ensure that the Ethernet cable for ij.start.canon ts9120 is attached to the right port of the printer and the router.
  • A menu tab on the left side is now displayed in the view panel of your printer. The house icon is marked. Click this tab. Press this tab.
  • In the left corner of the bottom of the screen, there will be a Wireless Connection tab. To open the wireless screen, press it.
  • The different possible choices are given on the next screen. Pick the tab LAN Settings.
  • Next, select the option Wired LAN.
  • Now tab on the Active/Inactive Wired LAN button.
  • By clicking on the tab, pick the “Active” status.
  • On the left side of the screen press the Menu button. Wait until the settings are completed. In the bottom left corner of your window, you can see the Ethernet button. After the link is complete, it will show.

Implement Pixma TS9120

  • To open the web tab, open an internet browser and type in http://canon.com/ijsetup.com/.
  • You are sent back to the Printer Configuration website of Canon. Click the Configuration page.
  • You should closely follow all guidelines and instructions on the computer.
  • Now the screen for the product range is opened. You need to type the product and click Go on Pixma TS9120
  • When asked to pick your country, determine your region correctly.
  • The download link is now open. Tap on the Register Download. The configuration file is downloaded from your computer.
  • The Save location for the downloaded file may be chosen or cannot be selected. You should do what you want.
  • The update can take a number of minutes. Wait for the same patient.
  • Select Execute on the file that is downloaded.

Canon Pixma ts9120 is installed for Windows

  • Open your computer’s Downloaded File.
  • There will appear a tiny Setup pane. To start setup, click on the tab Start.
  • You will be asked by the next screen to pick your location. Indicate the area concerned and press Next.
  • The Product Licensing Arrangement is now open to you. Download and pick yes.
  • Your approval for the Expanded Survey service will be asked via the following window. Read all the stuff. You will determine whether to consent or not. As per your decision, click on the option.
  • You are now taken to the window of the Firewall Configuration. The box you wish to uninstall must be labeled. Next click.
  • The selected Link form is shown next pane. The printer and router information must be checked. If the specifics are right, press Yes to continue.
  • The setup for your printer will begin. You may be asked for some information depending on the router and the network settings. The window may pop up with “Choose Wireless Router.” Pick the best router here, type your password or network key, and then press Next.
  • The state of setup is seen on the next screen as sorting. You have to wait for the procedure to be done.
  • You will be notified on the next window after it is finished. Next press on the Completed window of the Network Link.
  • The test print screen is now being redirected. Run the test with the instructions shown on the computer. Please notice that in order to run the test, your printer needs to be filled with plain paper.
  • On the complete Configuration Pane, press Next.
  • Your authorization to update additional applications will be required next window. Choose the right one and press Next.
  • On the corresponding pane, press Next again.
  • The user login window will now be taken. To bypass the processor, you can either press Skip, click Next to log. Follow the guidelines for registering yourself as a customer.
  • The final screen showing installation completion is displayed. To leave the installer, press Exit.
  • The ij.start.canon ts9120 has been completed from now on.

Canon ts9120 for Mac install

  • Open your computer’s downloaded file.
  • There will appear a tiny Setup pane. On this first screen, press Next.
  • Username and password will be given if necessary. If requested. Type in specifics and pick the Helper tab for Download.
  • On the Configuration pane, click on the Start Setup key.
  • You will now pick your area as soon as possible. You have to click Next to pick the right alternative.
  • The window of the Software License Accord will now appear. Download and pick yes.
  • The Expanded Survey Software is placed next to the doors. After progressing through the same, you can decide to agree or disagree. Tap on the alternative according to your choice.
  • The state of your printer will be tested by your Mac and this may take some time. Wait for it.
  • The Relation form is shown in a corresponding pane. Check if the details of the printer and router are right. If you’re right, tap Yes.
  • The setup for your printer will begin. You may need to take an additional move depending on the router and its settings. The window may pop up with “Choose Wireless Router.” Pick the right router here and type your password and then press Next.
  • You will be aware of the completion of the link on the following page. Next press on the Completed window of the Network Link.
  • The drivers start to load as seen on the next screen. Wait for it.
  • You will get a pop-up to check for network access. To smooth installation, press Allow.
  • You will be able to connect a Printer after successfully finishing the installation. Tap here for Add Printer.
  • A list of printers in the drop-down menu is shown in the Add Screen. Under the Kind tab, pick the multifunction Bonjour TS sequence. From the Usage List, you must pick AirPrint or Safe AirPrint.
  • Select Connect after finding the correct printer.
  • On the Add Screen, press Next.
  • The Test Print screen is now available. Run the test with the instructions shown on the computer. To run the test, make sure that you load the printer with basic paper.
  • On the complete Configuration Screen, press Next.
  • Your authorization to update additional applications will be required next window. Choose the right one and press Next.
  • On the corresponding pane, press Next again.
  • To Next press or Skip the user log window. You can register as a user or for now save the operation. Follow the guidelines for registering yourself as a customer.
  • To stop the installer, press Exit.
  • The ij.start.canon ts9120 has been completed from now on.
